criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Able to read and speak English;

          -  Has a smartphone;

          -  Lives in the Philadelphia area;

          -  Age 14 or older;

          -  Able to provide informed consent;

          -  Enrolled as a member of a 2 to 5 member family team with least one member 65 years or
             older.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Already participating in another physical activity study;

          -  An 18-month physical activity program is infeasible (e.g., metastatic cancer, unable
             to ambulate or provide informed consent) or unsafe (currently pregnant or told by a
             physician not to exercise);

          -  Do not have sufficient eyesight or dexterity to operate device;

          -  Average step count greater than 7,500 steps/day during the run-in period.
